[341.338106, "o", "=== Golden Gate Assembly Verification ===\r\n\r\nAfter PCR amplification with designed primers:\r\n\r\nFragment 1 (input backbone):\r\n  5'-[BsaI site]-N-TGAG-[backbone]-ACAT-N-[BsaI site]-3'\r\n  After BsaI digestion: 5'-TGAG-[backbone]-ACAT-3'\r\n\r\nFragment 2 (eGFP without stop):\r\n  5'-[BsaI site]-N-ACAT-[eGFP]-GGTA-N-[BsaI site]-3'\r\n  After BsaI digestion: 5'-ACAT-[eGFP]-GGTA-3'\r\n\r\n"]
[341.338425, "o", "Fragment 3 (FLAG without start/stop):\r\n  5'-[BsaI site]-N-GGTA-[FLAG]-GACA-N-[BsaI site]-3'\r\n  After BsaI digestion: 5'-GGTA-[FLAG]-GACA-3'\r\n\r\nFragment 4 (SNAP without start):\r\n  5'-[BsaI site]-N-GACA-[SNAP]-TGAG-N-[BsaI site]-3'\r\n  After BsaI digestion: 5'-GACA-[SNAP]-TGAG-3'\r\n\r\nAssembly order (via compatible overhangs):\r\n  Input (TGAG...ACAT) + eGFP (ACAT...GGTA) + FLAG (GGTA...GACA) + SNAP (GACA...TGAG)\r\n\r\nResult: Circular plasmid with fusion protein eGFP-FLAG-SNAP inserted into input\r\n\r\n✓ Assembly logic verified!\r\n"]
