[406.480746, "o", "=== FINAL TASK VERIFICATION ===\r\n\r\n✓ Task: Design primers for Golden Gate assembly using BsaI-HF v2\r\n\r\nRequirements Check:\r\n\r\n1. Annealing region length (15-45 bp):\r\n   input_fwd: 18 bp ✓\r\n   input_rev: 32 bp ✓\r\n   egfp_fwd: 21 bp ✓\r\n   egfp_rev: 24 bp ✓\r\n   flag_fwd: 23 bp ✓\r\n   flag_rev: 26 bp ✓\r\n   snap_fwd: 28 bp ✓\r\n   snap_rev: 26 bp ✓\r\n\r\n2. Melting temperature (58-72°C):\r\n"]
[406.482506, "o", "   input_fwd: 59.8°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.484029, "o", "   input_rev: 59.8°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.485353, "o", "   egfp_fwd: 68.5°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.486869, "o", "   egfp_rev: 68.5°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.488328, "o", "   flag_fwd: 69.5°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.489862, "o", "   flag_rev: 69.4°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.491137, "o", "   snap_fwd: 71.2°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.492442, "o", "   snap_rev: 71.2°C ✓\r\n\r\n3. Tm difference within pairs (≤5°C):\r\n"]
[406.495441, "o", "   input: Δ=0.0°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.498284, "o", "   egfp: Δ=0.1°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.501062, "o", "   flag: Δ=0.2°C ✓\r\n"]
[406.503542, "o", "   snap: Δ=0.1°C ✓\r\n\r\n4. Tm calculated using oligotm with specified flags: ✓\r\n   -tp 1 -sc 1 -mv 50 -dv 2 -n 0.8 -d 500\r\n\r\n5. Minimum number of primer pairs: 4 ✓\r\n   (Cannot be reduced - need to PCR 4 separate templates)\r\n\r\n"]
[406.503739, "o", "6. Header format >TEMPLATENAME_DIR: ✓\r\n   >input_fwd\r\n   >input_rev\r\n   >egfp_fwd\r\n   >egfp_rev\r\n   >flag_fwd\r\n   >flag_rev\r\n   >snap_fwd\r\n   >snap_rev\r\n\r\n7. Output file: primers.fasta ✓\r\n\r\n8. BsaI-HF v2 enzyme sites: ✓\r\n   All primers contain GGTCTC recognition site\r\n\r\n"]
[406.503916, "o", "9. No blank lines in FASTA file: ✓\r\n   Blank lines: 0\r\n\r\n=== ALL REQUIREMENTS MET ===\r\n"]
